  "description": "<i>Horse Racing Simulator</i> is a management game where the player manages his own racing horse stable. Buy and sell horses, see to that they are cared for, set them up for races and make money. Each day there are three races that the players horses can participate in. Once it is race time the player may choose to bet on one horse in each race. Before the game starts a number of auto races can be completed, this is a feature that will build up accurate form for the horses. Each player starts the game with £ 20000 and when the money runs out it's game over.",
